# ⚡ Voltix Video Player

A modern media player built with Python and PyQt6.

Voltix Video Player supports both video and audio playback with a clean interface, customizable controls, and future expansion features.

---

## 🎬 Features

### Media Playback
- MP4 Support
- MKV Support
- AVI Support
- MOV Support
- WMV Support
- WEBM Support
- MP3 Support
- WAV Support
- FLAC Support
- AAC Support
- OGG Support
- M4A Support

### Player Controls
- Play
- Pause
- Stop
- Open File
- Volume Control
- Seek Bar
- Time Display
- Fullscreen Mode

### User Interface
- Custom Voltix Branding
- Custom Window Icon
- Logo Display When No Media Is Loaded
- Responsive Layout

### Keyboard Shortcuts
| Key | Action |
|------|---------|
| Space | Play / Pause |
| O | Open File |
| F | Fullscreen |
| S | Settings |

### Settings System
- Saved Settings
- Configurable Volume
- Keybind System
- JSON-Based Configuration

