## 🛠 Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/VoltixVideoPlayer.git
```

### Enter Project Folder

```bash
cd VoltixVideoPlayer
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install PyQt6
```

### Run Voltix

```bash
python Voltix_Advanced.py
```

---

## 📦 Building An EXE

Install PyInstaller:

```bash
pip install pyinstaller
```

Build:

```bash
pyinstaller --clean --onefile --windowed --icon=logo.ico Voltix_Advanced.py
```

The executable will be located inside:

```text
dist/
```

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```text
VoltixVideoPlayer/
│
├── Voltix_Advanced.py
├── settings.json
├── logo.png
├── logo.ico
├── README.md
│
├── build/
├── dist/
└── __pycache__/
```

---

## ⚙ Settings File

Example:

```json
{
    "volume": 100,
    "keybinds": {
        "open": "O",
        "play_pause": "Space",
        "settings": "S",
        "fullscreen": "F"
    }
}
```

